        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>National Instant Criminal Background Check System (NICS) Data Integrity Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill modifies procedures for conducting firearms-related background checks through the national instant criminal background check system (NICS).</p> <p>Specifically, the bill requires the NICS to retain records related to a firearms-related background check for as long as necessary to determine whether an individual is eligible to receive a firearm.</p> <p>Additionally, the bill requires the NICS to query additional databases for relevant information, including the National Data Exchange, the Interstate Identification Index System, and the National Crime Information Center databases.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
